               <t:note>
                  <t:date type="foundation" notBefore="1500" notAfter="1600">1500-1600</t:date>
                  
                  <t:ab type="history">Dabr. 
                     Currently there are three churches at the site: a small church of St. <t:persName type="tabot" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">Mary</t:persName> on the peak of the rock (visible from <t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0185SGM">Sǝddayto</t:placeName>), an older and a recent churches below in the compound. Pre-historic rock paintings have been discovered in the vicinity of the site. 
</t:ab>
                  <t:ab type="tabot">
                     <t:measure quantity="6"/>Tābots (said to be 6 but only 3 were recalled): 
                     <t:persName type="tabot" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">Mary</t:persName>, one marble with many names inscribed, <t:persName type="tabot" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4377Gabriel">Gabriel</t:persName>.</t:ab>
                  <t:ab type="description">
