                        </t:graphic>
                     </t:figure>27 Mss. photographed: <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm001">TRM-001</t:ref> “The Faith of the Fathers”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm002">TRM-002</t:ref> “Synaxarion (March-September)”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm003">TRM-003</t:ref> “Miracles of Mary”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm004">TRM-004</t:ref> “Four Gospel, Golden Gospel”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm005">TRM-005</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm006">TRM-006</t:ref> “Miracles of the Trinity”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm007">TRM-007</t:ref> “Vita of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm008">TRM-008</t:ref> “Psalter”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm009">TRM-009</t:ref> “Psalter incomplete at the beginning.”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm010">TRM-010</t:ref> “Vita of Abunä Arägawi/ Vita Gäbrä Krǝstos”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm011">TRM-011</t:ref> “Vita of Abunä Arägawi/ Vita Gäbrä Krǝstos”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm012">TRM-012</t:ref> “Vita of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm013">TRM-013</t:ref> “Miracles of Mary/ Miracles of Jesus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm014">TRM-014</t:ref> “Homily on the Saviour of the World ”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm015">TRM-015</t:ref> “Miracles of Jesus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm016">TRM-016</t:ref> “Book of the Funeral Rite”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm017">TRM-017</t:ref> “Hymns of Mäwasʿǝt”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStrm018">TRM-018</t:ref> “Collection of Mälkǝʿ-Poetry”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="http